only getting her shot

01:31.694 --> 01:34.328
because she's a woman,
go ahead, but let's be real.

01:34.363 --> 01:36.330
If you're saying that, you're a man.

01:36.365 --> 01:39.533
You're a backwards-thinking,
backwards-cap-wearing,

01:39.569 --> 01:41.435
male-pattern-baldness-hiding man.

01:41.471 --> 01:44.105
So, bitch and moan all you want,
gentlemen, but tonight,

01:44.140 --> 01:46.640
a girl's gonna be the lead
sports story in the world.

01:46.675 --> 01:48.708
And if that upsets you, well,

01:48.743 --> 01:50.276
maybe you're just getting your period.

01:50.312 --> 01:51.611
Go get 'em, Ginny!

01:51.646 --> 01:53.146
